snippet.textDisplay:
Close fight. Here's my takings from it as I also watched the full fight:
- Very closely matched but comeon this was no robbery
- Jones isn't very liked as a person and I imagine this is having an impact in reviewing the fight objectively
- Yes one of the judges was bonkers but at worst I would call it win by Jones and at best a draw.
- Reyes really gassed out toward the end and frankly round 3 wasn't as clear cut as many are suggesting.


Thing is Reyes was striking alot more but not every strike was a clean shot.


Rematch very much needed.
